name: Cyber Ebil Nano-Katana Cape (AC)
description: After years of testing, and countless dead test subjects, EbilCorp has decided to release the Nanobite Cape and Katanas to all of its assassins. While the cape acts like a shield; side effects may include but are not limited to: death, nausea, memory loss, hearing, loss, hunger, starvation, and loss in vision.
